                                          Trusted Url
                                      --------------------

      Trusted Url :- It explicitly authorizes the browser to load external resources (like APIs, images, or iframes) 
                     directly within a Lightning Web Component (LWC) without being blocked by browser security restrictions.

        example: - calling public api like indian postal code from LWC browse will block the endpoint url so need to add
                    the url in the Trusted Url and make the check box check for connect src script.
